data.description: Beautiful well-maintained farmhouse with 3 bedroom and 2 bathrooms. Home sits far back from the road with beautiful oak trees throughout the property of over 2 acres. As you walk into the front door you see the wood-tile throughout the home and farmhouse kitchen. Walking out of the backdoor onto the covered and gated back porch to see out to the huge back yard. Large 36x54 barn with 100 amp service with plenty of storage space for your outdoor toys/RV/boats. Behind the barn is more land fenced off and separated to give you additional privacy and space for all of your needs. Close to parks, schools and grocery store. Schedule a showing today.  Seller is a licensed real estate agent
